Did Wesley Snipes intentionally trick Billy Blanks into missing his Passenger 57 audition, thus securing Wesley the role and cornering Billy into a career of producing workout tapes? Hard to say, but Langston and his guest Roy Wood Jr. (The Daily Show on Comedy Central) intend to find out.
